Articles.Content: My school has a first robotics FRC team and I would like to know who in the KSP community has heard of First.

I was a mentor for many many Years with FRC Team 294 Beach city robotics.

I also was a member of team MSAC for the first ever VEX college challenge..

(I work with robotics at a automation company now ) Old and fast times .
I should have said this in the OP, I'm on team 4485 tribe tech.
